---
// No external data needed
---

<section class="trust" aria-labelledby="trust-h">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="trust__header">
      <p class="section-label fade-up" style="color:var(--cyan);">Confianza</p>
      <h2 class="section-h2 fade-up" id="trust-h">Comprás con tranquilidad</h2>
      <p class="trust__sub">Cada equipo Puraqua viene respaldado por garantía, soporte real y envío a todo el país.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="trust__inner fade-up" role="list">
      <div class="trust__badge" role="listitem">
        <div class="trust__badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><rect x="4" y="8" width="28" height="20" rx="6" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M12 18h12M18 13v10" stroke="#00c8e0" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="trust__badge-t">Envíos a todo Uruguay</div>
          <div class="trust__badge-s">Montevideo y el interior del país.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust__badge" role="listitem">
        <div class="trust__badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><path d="M18 4L6 9v10c0 7.6 5.1 14.7 12 16.5C24.9 33.7 30 26.6 30 19V9L18 4z" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M13 18l3.5 3.5L23 15" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="trust__badge-t">12 meses de garantía</div>
          <div class="trust__badge-s">Si algo falla, lo resolvemos.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust__badge" role="listitem">
        <div class="trust__badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><circle cx="18" cy="18" r="14" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M14 18l3 3 5-5" stroke="#10b981" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="trust__badge-t">Soporte por WhatsApp</div>
          <div class="trust__badge-s">Antes y después de la compra.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="trust__badge" role="listitem">
        <div class="trust__badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 36 36" fill="none"><rect x="6" y="10" width="24" height="16" rx="4" stroke="#2c6faa" stroke-width="1.5"/><path d="M10 18h16M10 22h8" stroke="#5ba3d9" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="26" cy="14" r="3" fill="rgba(0,200,224,.3)" stroke="#00c8e0" stroke-width="1"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="trust__badge-t">Pago seguro</div>
          <div class="trust__badge-s">MercadoPago con todas las tarjetas.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .trust { padding: 64px 0; background: var(--white); border-top: 1px solid var(--border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .trust__header { text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px; }
  .trust__sub { color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 10px; max-width: 440px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; font-size: .95rem; }
  .trust__inner { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 40px; justify-content: center; align-items: center; }
  .trust__badge {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px;
    padding: 18px 28px; border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--white);
    transition: box-shadow .2s, transform .2s;
    min-width: 200px;
  }
  .trust__badge:hover { box-shadow: var(--shadow-md); transform: translateY(-2px); }
  .trust__badge-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
  .trust__badge-t { font-family: var(--font-head); font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--blue-dark); }
  .trust__badge-s { font-size: .78rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 2px; }
</style>
